<h1>About The Cerf Report</h1>
<p class="subtitle">More signal. Less noise.</p>

<p>
<strong>The Cerf Report</strong> is an independent publication and podcast focused on clear,
evidence-driven analysis across technology, economics, geopolitics, and AI.
The goal is to cut through narrative noise and explain the structural forces shaping
markets and power.
</p>

